{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fe0e9fb0a3","title":"对卫立煌来电的批语和复电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6823a4a25d","index":0,"year":1955,"month":3,"day":17,"articleId":"fe0e9fb0a3"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"9a078f7b3f","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"fe0e9fb0a3","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"卫立煌，字俊如，原国民党军将领。解放战争后期，担任国民党军东北“总”总司令，因没有积极执行蒋介石的作战命令，被软禁于南京。1949年1月蒋介石引退后卫去香港，1955年3月回国。1955年3月16日，卫立煌从广州致电毛泽东：“立煌昨日返回祖国，平安抵穗，谨电致敬，并问候刘委员长、周总理、朱副主席及中央各位先生。”"},{"id":"699199d28c","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"fe0e9fb0a3","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央副秘书长、中央办公厅主任。"}],"contents":[{"id":"d14a5a9bdf","type":"title","text":"对卫立焊来电\"的批语和复电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"fe0e9fb0a3"},{"id":"9a078f7b3f","type":"paragraph","text":"尚昆P：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"fe0e9fb0a3"},{"id":"699199d28c","type":"paragraph","text":"应发一电表示欢迎。由华南分局派适当干部好好护送来京。如他愿意在广州长沙武汉郑州等处（或走上海天津）看看建设情况，应先电告各处好好引导招待，并表示热情欢迎态度","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"fe0e9fb0a3"},{"id":"55c8a83ec8","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"fe0e9fb0a3"},{"id":"b619375928","type":"paragraph","text":"三月十七日早广州华南分局即送卫俊如先生","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"fe0e9fb0a3"},{"id":"729dde67a2","type":"paragraph","text":"三月十六日电报收到。先生返国，甚表欢迎，盼早日来京，借图良唔。如有兴趣，可于沿途看看情况，于本月底或下月初到京，也是好的。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"fe0e9fb0a3"},{"id":"f1689b643b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"fe0e9fb0a3"},{"id":"4a04c8e97f","type":"paragraph","text":"三月十七日","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"fe0e9fb0a3"}],"page":{"id":"01b042d546","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"fe0e9fb0a3","start":494,"end":495}}}},"__N_SSG":true}